{"tid":480422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（人辦) 支那土豪有樣睇？","createTime":"2017-11-26T07:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T23:54:12.000Z","uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d1cf1e65cb5ca7982216943abf60f9e7360e8797","tid":480422,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"支那土豪就係有一陣土味，就算唔使睇樣都分得出「他來自支那」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 鐘意拎雞那咁大隻字印晒牌子名既斜咩袋/tote bag<br />\n<br />\n2. 鐘意著印有巨型馬仔logo既polo tee<br />\n<br />\n3. 錶一定有金色，仲要加鑽石係錶面<br />\n<br />\n4. 手機、平版一定要金色<br />\n<br />\n5. 一定要金絲眼鏡框<br />\n<br />\n6. 電髮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/150201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F150201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1557ea1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"284623f3330536e07a49c23a5a74130ee8358fcb","tid":480422,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"盧海鵬扮嘅"},{"pid":"40166ff7aae2e6e9dbcaa0a084b2b4b056ccff8e","tid":480422,"uid":48157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:16:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26812181608fb2a14e4687818d3b9125f13efb69","tid":480422,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想講<br />\n<br />\n土豪唔會搭交通工具.....</blockquote><br />\n呢個係底級土豪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻錶又唔係江c單頓，個袋又唔係愛馬士，&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"35f2909e84b04746f88b2cc62be9c12c5e1bf34e","tid":480422,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022cd02c1404800134f71340050046942b3a4bd1","tid":480422,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"邊忽豪"},{"pid":"a8a8b6ff34341775d066efe362a73f9c5a4cbea3","